1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:04,864
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,864 --> 00:00:10,368
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,368 --> 00:00:16,796
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,796 --> 00:00:21,276
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,276 --> 00:00:25,724
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,724 --> 00:00:30,635
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,635 --> 00:00:34,684
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,684 --> 00:00:39,219
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,219 --> 00:00:43,516
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,516 --> 00:00:48,281
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,281 --> 00:00:51,772
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,772 --> 00:00:55,452
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,098 --> 00:01:00,476
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,476 --> 00:01:03,164
=Episode 23=

15
00:01:06,133 --> 00:01:08,733
You may leave now.

16
00:01:10,166 --> 00:01:13,633
Your daughter is as proud as you.

17
00:01:16,233 --> 00:01:17,833
Your child is outstanding.

18
00:01:19,233 --> 00:01:20,433
She has also changed

19
00:01:21,333 --> 00:01:23,433
my view on people and many things.

20
00:01:25,233 --> 00:01:27,933
I want to apologize

21
00:01:28,566 --> 00:01:29,766
for my previous words and actions.

22
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,766
That's alright.

23
00:01:33,033 --> 00:01:35,200
You have twin daughters, right?

24
00:01:40,833 --> 00:01:42,133
Jin Xi'er.

25
00:01:43,766 --> 00:01:46,566
So, are you planning to go overseas
for further development now?

26
00:01:46,566 --> 00:01:47,424
Yes.

27
00:01:48,233 --> 00:01:52,433
I see. So you have experience
working overseas.

28
00:01:52,433 --> 00:01:55,133
And you've won the world championship
in mixed martial arts.

29
00:01:55,133 --> 00:01:56,200
Yes.

30
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:59,233
Well, you have an impressive resume.

31
00:02:00,133 --> 00:02:03,033
And you satisfy my needs.

32
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:06,400
How about you fly over
next month for onboarding?

33
00:02:07,366 --> 00:02:08,864
Thank you.

34
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:21,133
What? Are you reluctant
to leave your hometown?

35
00:02:22,633 --> 00:02:26,333
No, I need a change of scene.

36
00:02:27,166 --> 00:02:30,000
Is it because of your boyfriend?

37
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,500
No.

38
00:02:42,966 --> 00:02:44,400
Since I took over the company,

39
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,900
you've been helping me.

40
00:02:47,433 --> 00:02:48,700
Without your help,

41
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:51,333
I might have been sidelined
by Mei Xiangfa and others.

42
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:54,800
Mr. Lan, you are one of top young men
in Horton City.

43
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,433
You are truly capable.

44
00:02:57,200 --> 00:03:00,400
Besides, helping you is helping myself.

45
00:03:01,166 --> 00:03:05,500
The better the group develops,
the better for all of us, right?

46
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:08,900
I have no problem on the time.

47
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,433
We must get the investment

48
00:03:11,833 --> 00:03:13,033
from Lihuai International.

49
00:03:13,033 --> 00:03:14,528
Yes.

50
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:17,500
You take care of
the press conference and

51
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:20,766
my confession.

52
00:03:21,033 --> 00:03:24,800
Okay. Mr. Lan, honestly,

53
00:03:24,966 --> 00:03:28,000
I hope you and Miss Jin can be together,

54
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:34,166
because I also don't like the Gu family
interfering in your family affairs.

55
00:04:00,733 --> 00:04:02,133
I'm sorry, Mr. Lan, I...

56
00:04:05,566 --> 00:04:06,966
I accidentally fell asleep.

57
00:04:09,566 --> 00:04:10,633
No problem.

58
00:04:11,966 --> 00:04:13,333
You must be too tired.

59
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:19,366
Get ready. Let's go somewhere.

60
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,200
Where are we going?

61
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:30,933
Who's working in my
company today, Jin Xi'en

62
00:04:32,533 --> 00:04:36,000
or your older daughter who won the world
championship in mixed martial arts?

63
00:04:43,166 --> 00:04:45,433
When will you stop deceiving my son?

64
00:04:49,133 --> 00:04:51,233
My younger daughter joined your company.

65
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:52,966
That's why we moved to this city.

66
00:04:53,033 --> 00:04:55,366
We have never planned to deceive anyone.

67
00:04:59,166 --> 00:05:03,933
My little girl was treated unfairly
in your company.

68
00:05:04,966 --> 00:05:08,000
What's wrong with my older daughter
stepping up to help her?

69
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:13,700
Later, she helped the company
get rid of the mole

70
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:15,800
and also solved the crisis
of false accounts.

71
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:19,800
You tell me what mistakes we made.

72
00:05:22,833 --> 00:05:25,800
She put in time and energy

73
00:05:26,033 --> 00:05:27,900
and successfully completed the work.

74
00:05:28,933 --> 00:05:31,366
She comes home late at night

75
00:05:31,533 --> 00:05:32,933
and even risks her reputation.

76
00:05:32,933 --> 00:05:34,766
Why didn't she resign then?

77
00:05:39,100 --> 00:05:41,800
Because my little girl fell for Mr. Lan.

78
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,600
Every family has its own problems.

79
00:06:02,533 --> 00:06:03,933
It seems I can't interfere

80
00:06:05,633 --> 00:06:07,233
in their affairs.

81
00:06:08,033 --> 00:06:09,700
Let them pursue their own happiness.

82
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:14,400
Which one of your daughters
does my son like?

83
00:06:18,766 --> 00:06:20,233
I will tell my son.

84
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,533
I don't want him to be kept in the dark.

85
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:27,566
I suggest letting it run its course.

86
00:06:29,433 --> 00:06:31,166
You can't hide the truth.

87
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:45,766
I hope my son will marry Gu Qianqian,

88
00:06:50,433 --> 00:06:52,200
but I like your daughters more.

89
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:58,433
- I mean it.
- Hope to see you again.

90
00:06:59,166 --> 00:07:00,966
I'll bring you some good tea next time.

91
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:03,433
Your tea isn't very good.

92
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:10,533
I have to go.

93
00:07:10,533 --> 00:07:11,700
Okay.

94
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:13,333
Keep in touch.

95
00:07:13,333 --> 00:07:15,100
- Thanks for coming today.
- Thank you.

96
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:17,833
Oh, there's a beautiful garden
on the rooftop.

97
00:07:18,033 --> 00:07:19,133
You can take a look.

98
00:07:19,533 --> 00:07:21,166
Perhaps it will lift your spirits.

99
00:07:23,776 --> 00:07:25,166
I'm leaving.

100
00:07:25,166 --> 00:07:26,300
Ok. Take care.

101
00:07:26,666 --> 00:07:27,840
Thank you.

102
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:06,333
The confession
I look forward to the most?

103
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:16,966
On the rooftop,

104
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:26,033
(the man I love confesses
to me, holding 99 roses.)

105
00:08:37,366 --> 00:08:38,500
Every day I spend with you

106
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:43,100
is the most wonderful for me.

107
00:08:47,366 --> 00:08:48,600
You're like the sunshine,

108
00:08:49,966 --> 00:08:51,366
shining into my life.

109
00:08:54,766 --> 00:08:56,500
Although I'm too perfect,

110
00:08:58,133 --> 00:08:59,833
you're not scared away by my brilliance.

111
00:09:01,333 --> 00:09:02,533
Although you always hit me,

112
00:09:04,566 --> 00:09:06,000
I've suddenly gotten used to it.

113
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:12,566
After meeting you, I learned to trust,

114
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:18,000
to be myself, and to love.

115
00:09:20,433 --> 00:09:22,366
I remember the starry sky
we watched together.

116
00:09:24,233 --> 00:09:25,504
It was so beautiful.

117
00:09:26,733 --> 00:09:27,800
I suddenly realized

118
00:09:28,933 --> 00:09:30,966
the person I want to stargaze with

119
00:09:32,633 --> 00:09:35,600
is you, Jin Xi'en.

120
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:45,344
Thank you.

121
00:10:03,433 --> 00:10:06,800
Why?

122
00:10:07,233 --> 00:10:09,100
Why it happened to me?

123
00:10:12,500 --> 00:10:16,333
(Why? Why did this happen to me?)

124
00:10:42,633 --> 00:10:43,904
What's so funny?

125
00:10:44,133 --> 00:10:47,000
This is the first time
I've seen you so unhappy.

126
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,400
Why are you here, Mr. Zeng?

127
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:58,800
I came to see you.
Mr. Lan confesses today.

128
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:00,633
How did you know?

129
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:09,900
You missed the press conference.

130
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:11,900
(The above is the objective truth.)

131
00:11:14,233 --> 00:11:18,166
(At today's press conference,
I have good news to share.)

132
00:11:18,433 --> 00:11:22,833
(My girlfriend is my secretary,
Jin Xi'en.)

133
00:11:26,233 --> 00:11:27,233
Unbelievable.

134
00:11:28,333 --> 00:11:30,100
What on earth was he thinking?

135
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:35,566
I knew you would give him
to your sister.

136
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:43,166
Feeling down? How about a drink?

137
00:11:47,233 --> 00:11:49,233
Come on. Let's go.

138
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,728
Go ahead.

139
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:17,120
Miss Jin.

140
00:12:18,633 --> 00:12:22,166
What's your decision about my job offer?

141
00:12:22,433 --> 00:12:25,433
I'm sorry, Mr. Zeng.
I appreciate your kindness.

142
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,766
I want to do something right for me.

143
00:12:32,033 --> 00:12:34,400
I have decided to work
as a boxing coach abroad.

144
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,633
That's good. By the way,

145
00:12:41,433 --> 00:12:42,900
I have something else to tell you.

146
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:46,100
Apart from the bills from Li Yuan,

147
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:47,833
there's basically no problem

148
00:12:47,833 --> 00:12:49,566
with the rest coming from Lan Chen.

149
00:12:52,533 --> 00:12:54,933
There are financial problems
within your company,

150
00:12:55,966 --> 00:12:58,166
but Lan Chen has been open and honest.

151
00:12:58,566 --> 00:13:00,766
He promised
to turn a profit tenfold next year.

152
00:13:01,100 --> 00:13:02,233
I really admire him.

153
00:13:04,833 --> 00:13:07,966
I suspect there is still a mole
inside your group.

154
00:13:09,566 --> 00:13:11,100
Tell your sister to be more careful.

155
00:13:12,233 --> 00:13:13,300
Could it be Li Yuan?

156
00:13:14,333 --> 00:13:17,533
I don't think so.
He may have just been used.

157
00:13:18,700 --> 00:13:20,700
I think it's someone else.

158
00:13:25,366 --> 00:13:26,656
Excuse me.

159
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:31,933
Hello, Uncle. Yes.

160
00:13:33,133 --> 00:13:35,133
I found the best expert, Dr. He Hao.

161
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:38,533
He will come later,
so let's call it off this week.

162
00:13:39,533 --> 00:13:41,766
Okay, I understand. Don't worry.

163
00:13:44,066 --> 00:13:45,300
Who is it?

164
00:13:45,300 --> 00:13:47,933
Qianqian's father, my uncle.

165
00:13:48,966 --> 00:13:50,733
He asked me
to find a doctor for Gu Qianqian.

166
00:13:51,533 --> 00:13:52,700
What's wrong with her?

167
00:13:52,933 --> 00:13:55,366
Nothing, but I can't tell you now.

168
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,533
Eat something.

169
00:13:58,566 --> 00:14:02,633
By the way. Mr. Zeng, how is
the financing plan of WE Beauty Group?

170
00:14:03,833 --> 00:14:05,566
It's a bad plan.

171
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:08,400
Impossible. Mr. Lan
and I both think the plan is good.

172
00:14:11,433 --> 00:14:14,966
If you think so,
I'll have nothing to say.

173
00:14:21,208 --> 00:14:23,072
♪You fell into my heart♪

174
00:14:23,072 --> 00:14:25,500
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

175
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:26,766
Miss Jin!

176
00:14:26,766 --> 00:14:28,488
♪Open my secret♪

177
00:14:28,488 --> 00:14:34,720
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

178
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:37,666
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

179
00:14:37,666 --> 00:14:39,499
Why?

180
00:14:39,499 --> 00:14:44,400
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

181
00:14:45,423 --> 00:14:49,945
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

182
00:14:52,975 --> 00:14:57,936
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

183
00:15:00,985 --> 00:15:06,809
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

184
00:15:06,809 --> 00:15:14,279
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

185
00:15:14,279 --> 00:15:17,760
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

186
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:21,881
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

187
00:15:21,881 --> 00:15:23,577
♪Open my secret♪

188
00:15:23,577 --> 00:15:29,625
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

189
00:15:29,625 --> 00:15:33,497
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

190
00:15:33,497 --> 00:15:38,003
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

191
00:15:38,003 --> 00:15:46,713
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
